reviewText: I bought this DVD many years ago in a dollar store and still have it, I was in vacation and did it faithfully every morning it took about 45 mins to 1 he to do entire tape but I did lose 30lbs after about 3 months, I had tons of energy and now looking for something new along with this dvd, It looks like it's from the 70's and definitely was not made in the US but it's worth the but if you stick to it.
